items.sentence: It would be nice to spend some time with Tom.
I want to do everything possible to help Tom.
I don't want Tom to get the wrong impression.
What did you and Tom talk about this morning?
Would you mind helping Tom with his homework?
Why did you pretend you'd never heard of Tom?
Why haven't you talked to Tom about this yet?
I never thought Tom would want to go with us.
What would you do if you were in Tom's place?
There were at least three people in the park.
